        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 28 at 3:23PM MDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 323 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Tatum, moving north at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Tatum.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
